	(text "From ST7789VW datasheet:\n- IM[2:0] = 'b000: 8-bit parallel, data on DAT[7:0]\n- IM[2:0] = 'b110: 4-line serial, data on SDA.\nIn serial, DCX (LCD_RS) is the clock input, and WRX (LCD_CLK)\nbecomes the register select. See tables in \"8.4.1 Pin description\""
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 156.21 213.36 0)
		(effects
